Class RectangularComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.components.Component
      • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.components.RectangularComponent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImageComponent, RectComponent

    public abstract class RectangularComponent
extends Component
    The RectangularComponent is an abstract Component implementing basic functionality for Components that are rectangular.
